description: VA - Pure 80's: Headbangers Rule! [2007] DVD5 A selection of '80s music videos from the heavy metal genre are included on this collection Pure 80's Headbangers Rule video. This DVD includes music videos by Rainbow, Dio, Scorpions, Y&T, Cinderella, TNT, Queensryche, Kingdom Come, Yngwie J. Malmsteen's Rising Force, Extreme, Tora Tora, Great White, Bang Tango, L.A. Guns, and Faith No More. Pure 80's Headbangers Rule movie was released Jan 23, 2007 by the Universal Music & Video Distribution studio.
